      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "OAKLEY LANE (1) filled a minor placing last start at Gunnedah behind Clocking On (20.29) in a Maiden. Has the early speed to land on the pace and can stick on. Likely to feature again. SHE'S A ANGEL (3) is still a maiden after 17 runs but rarely far away, the latest finishing out of the placings when fifth at Maitland. Remains without a win from the draw but has been in the placings two times from four attempts. Should be thereabouts. REBEL ENERGY (2) is overdue for a maiden success having placed at three of 10 starts, the latest missing the frame when fourth at this track. Expected to run well. ANOTHER ARTIST (5) is a John Taylor-trained newcomer by Bullet Train out of Exit Button. Start all important. Profiles well so pay to keep very safe.",
